                        <expectedResult><![CDATA[2. 웹페이지에서 로그아웃되며 로그아웃 메시지가 노출된다.<br><img src="https://cloudfront.tm4j.smartbear.com/tenant/81120b90-3fbe-3aea-8c23-510ce21bc0f8/project/10164/15c1bb93-f63d-42ff-86ff-39a9c32df9cd-1779351248903-1779351248903.png" style="width: 300px;" class="fr-fic fr-fil fr-dib fr-shadow" data-fr-last-image-pasted="true">]]></expectedResult>
