            <testScript type="steps">
                <steps>
                    <step index="0">
                        <customFields/>
                        <description><![CDATA[<strong>[검색바 placeholder 확인]<br></strong><br><br>1. 상단 검색 바 palceholder를 확인한다.]]></description>
                        <expectedResult><![CDATA[1. <strong>실습할 콘텐츠를 검색해보</strong><strong>세요.</strong>가 출력된다.<img src="https://cloudfront.tm4j.smartbear.com/tenant/81120b90-3fbe-3aea-8c23-510ce21bc0f8/project/10164/276cc5a4-a2de-4c6d-bdcd-4869271c9261-1777337528989-1777337528989.png" style="width: 302px;" class="fr-fic fr-fil fr-dib fr-shadow">]]></expectedResult>
                        <testData><![CDATA[]]></testData>
                    </step>
                    <step index="1">
                        <customFields/>
                        <description><![CDATA[<strong>[검색어가 없는 경우 검색 기능 확인]</strong><br><br><br>1. 검색 바에 아무것도 입력하지 않고 [돋보기] 버튼을 클릭한다.<br><img src="https://cloudfront.tm4j.smartbear.com/tenant/81120b90-3fbe-3aea-8c23-510ce21bc0f8/project/10164/27a2620f-4bc7-4f1c-9a1a-b39456630486-1764566113585-1764566113585.png" style="width: 41px;" class="fr-fic fr-fil fr-dib fr-shadow"><br>2. 검색 바에 아무것도 입력하지 않고 [enter]를 클릭한다.]]></description>
                        <expectedResult><![CDATA[1.&nbsp;<a href="https://metademy.ac/contents">콘텐츠&nbsp;</a>페이지로 이동한다.<br><br>2.&nbsp;<a href="https://metademy.ac/contents" data-pasted="true">콘텐츠&nbsp;</a>페이지로 이동한다.]]></expectedResult>
                        <testData><![CDATA[]]></testData>
                    </step>
                    <step index="2">
                        <customFields/>
                        <description><![CDATA[<strong>[검색 결과가 있는 경우]</strong><br><br><br>1. 검색 바에 '간호' 입력 후 [돋보기] 버튼을 클릭한다.<br><br>2. 검색 바에 '간호' 입력 후 [enter]를 클릭한다.<br><br>3. [보건 의료] 카테고리 버튼 클릭한다.<br><br>4. [생체 해부 실습] 소분류 클릭한다.<br><br>]]></description>
                        <expectedResult><![CDATA[1,2. 내용 및 이미지를 확인한다.<br><br><table style="width: 101%; height: 100px; margin: auto; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid;"><thead><tr><th>내용</th><th>이미지</th></tr></thead><colgroup><col style="width: 34.0625%;"><col style="width: 65.9375%;"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td>검색 바에&nbsp;<strong>간호&nbsp;</strong>text가 잔여해 있다.<br></td><td><img src="https://cloudfront.tm4j.smartbear.com/tenant/81120b90-3fbe-3aea-8c23-510ce21bc0f8/project/10164/32ba16e6-7928-4415-8a75-04f4fe7aa362-1777337622528-1777337622528.png" style="width: 300px;" class="fr-fic fr-fil fr-dib fr-shadow"></td></tr><tr><td>상단에 <strong data-pasted="true">간호</strong> <strong>(으)로 검색한 결과입니다.</strong> 가 출력된다.<br></td><td><img src="https://cloudfront.tm4j.smartbear.com/tenant/81120b90-3fbe-3aea-8c23-510ce21bc0f8/project/10164/c08c0e93-cefc-4508-b768-43b1659f602c-1764569698218-1764569698218.png" style="padding: 0px 1px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; cursor: pointer; user-select: none; box-shadow: rgb(204, 204, 204) 10px 10px 5px 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(9, 30, 66); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.07px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; width: 175px;" data-pasted="true" class="fr-fil fr-dib"><br><br></td></tr><tr><td><strong>간호술기(동작인식특화)</strong>가 검색된다.</td><td><img src="https://cloudfront.tm4j.smartbear.com/tenant/81120b90-3fbe-3aea-8c23-510ce21bc0f8/project/10164/f08c7410-1b8d-4b81-9500-8e71798aaf4b-1777338289626-1777338289625.png" style="width: 300px;" class="fr-fic fr-fil fr-dib fr-shadow"></td></tr><tr><td><strong>전체,보건 의료 실습,생체 해부 실습</strong> 소분류가 노출된다<br></td><td><img src="https://cloudfront.tm4j.smartbear.com/tenant/81120b90-3fbe-3aea-8c23-510ce21bc0f8/project/10164/f08c7410-1b8d-4b81-9500-8e71798aaf4b-1777338496416-1777338496416.png" style="width: 300px;" class="fr-fic fr-fil fr-dib fr-shadow"></td></tr><tr><td><strong>empty case&nbsp;</strong>위에 소분류가 노출된다<br></td><td><img src="https://cloudfront.tm4j.smartbear.com/tenant/81120b90-3fbe-3aea-8c23-510ce21bc0f8/project/10164/fb277ff5-c64f-4359-bb60-0c73dc4c5985-1777339419168-1777339419168.png" style="width: 300px;" class="fr-fic fr-fil fr-dib"></td></tr></tbody></table><br><br><br><br>]]></expectedResult>
                    </step>
                    <step index="3">
